{"pageProps":{"problem":{"id":"t4-train-2","grade":"7","semester":"up","category":"有理数","title":"针对训练2：绝对值性质应用","difficulty":3,"tags":["绝对值","性质"],"content":"若 $|a| = 2$，$|b| = 5$，且 $ab < 0$，求 $a - b$ 的值。","steps":[{"title":"确定 a、b 的值","content":"$|a| = 2 \\Rightarrow a = \\pm 2$\n\n$|b| = 5 \\Rightarrow b = \\pm 5$\n\n由 $ab < 0$ 知 $a$、$b$ 异号","formula":"a \\text{ 和 } b \\text{ 异号}"},{"title":"分类讨论","content":"① 若 $a = 2$，$b = -5$：$a - b = 2 - (-5) = 7$\n\n② 若 $a = -2$，$b = 5$：$a - b = -2 - 5 = -7$","formula":"a - b = 7 \\text{ 或 } a - b = -7"}]},"id":"t4-train-2"},"__N_SSG":true}